reviews.text: It was really good. better than Colorado springs McDonald's.. Everything was fresh thank you

The coke machine is always broken, service is crapy, and the wait is not worth the food. You could go somewhere for better food and get it faster. If you are in a rush go somewhere else, this place is not worth it. To top it all off it is not kid friendly anymore. They have electronic devices that don’t even work half the time. I went once and a baby got run over by a high chair. NOT kid friendly at all.
My weakness! Always a crowd but worth the wait. This location one of the cleanest for being so busy.
Wow looks really nice, so modern, good customer service and they have some good deals.

Nasty food..filthy restaurant .. I am so fed up with the sorry excuse for customer service. I came in today and ordered chicken nuggets, no dipping sauce but 2 packs of mayo, they charged me for the mayo, then tried to give me someone elses food. after they handed my food to the car in front of me, they gave me the same food without replacing it. This place is a horrible location. I will never go back to this location. The sad thing is the owners could care less.

I wasn't really a fan of the food here. I ordered fruit crepes, and the egg flavor was too much for me. Then, I got pancakes and they weren't cooked thoroughly. I didn't complain because I'd already sent my crepes back and my server was so sweet and accommodating.

Always good food and service when I come here. If you're a coffee lover, you'll be in love with the variety of choice brews they have available.  I always order the same thing..lol..classic breakfast.  Can't go wrong with bacon and eggs.

i got the nachos as a starter they were excellent (as usual), pancakes were fluffy ... eggs left something to be desired.  all in all good spot. 
however NO GRITS

Great coffee and pretty good service. They get pretty busy sometimes, and can forget items you ordered, but the wait staff is pleasant. The food is usually good, with vegan and gluten free options available. Parking is easy and convenient. The bottomless coffee is well worth it.
Chicken and Waffles at 3:00 am are amazing! It is a great atmosphere, delicious food, friendly staff and open late. What could be better!?!
